# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of microservices or proprietary apps, it may be ignored.
#   Uncomment the next line to ignore it:
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   According to poetry's documentation, poetry.lock should be tracked.
#   Uncomment the next line to ignore it:
#poetry.lock

# pdm
#   According to pdm documentation, pdm.lock should be tracked.
#   Uncomment the next line to ignore it:
#pdm.lock

